Lean Startup is considered standard startup canon and gives a great overview of the meta of the startup processes and finding product-market fit. I reread it every now and then to get into the right iterative mindset.

Eric was actually a student in Steve Blank's class. Most of the ideas in the lean startup are based on the customer development methodology that Steve developed.

