### [Actionable Gamification - Yu-Kai Chou](https://www.amazon.com/Actionable-Gamification-Beyond-Points-Leaderboards/dp/1511744049/)

<% link_to "https://www.amazon.com/Actionable-Gamification-Beyond-Points-Leaderboards/dp/1511744049/" do %>
